The dean met us for dinner to discuss the difficulty of the project and determine our next duty.
（院長和我們一起吃晚餐，討論這個計畫的困難點，並確定我們接下來的職責。）
Over the past decade, we have discovered different ways to develop new products that make a real difference.
（在過去的十年中，我們發現了開發新產品的不同方法，並產生了真正的影響。）
I don't dare to doubt your design for the theater, as this drama will surely draw a huge crowd.
